pi to R is 2 pi periodic.

00:03:10.305 --> 00:03:15.560 align:middle line:90%


00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:22.270 align:middle line:84%
And so, the question
that arose due to Fourier

00:03:22.270 --> 00:03:24.990 align:middle line:90%
in his study of heat transfer--

00:03:24.990 --> 00:03:29.600 align:middle line:84%
so this is Fourier,
I don't know,

00:03:29.600 --> 00:03:31.040 align:middle line:90%
something like 200 years ago.

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:37.980 align:middle line:90%


00:03:37.980 --> 00:03:45.750 align:middle line:84%
